# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [0.1.2]

### Added

- Improve cli
  - targets argument can take multiple values
  - Add cli description
  - Help shows default values
  - New option `--ingore` to ignore files by pattern
  - New option `--ingore-extend` to extend default ignore pattern
  - New option `--version` to show version
- Add tests for cli

### Fixed

- Only format files with `.md` extension
- Use recursive glob to find files

### Added

- Support for style parameters in images for Material for MkDocs
- Add text wrapping and formatting with mdwrap pre-commit hook

## [0.1.1] - 2023-07-12

### Added

- Support for style parameters in images for Material for MkDocs
- Add text wrapping and formatting with mdwrap pre-commit hook

## [0.1.0] - 2023-07-12

### Added

- Markdown wrapping
- Martial for MkDocs support
- Basic formatting (duplicate newlines and trailing whitespace)
- Unit tests and integration tests
